      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont even know why im typing this. i just feel so incredibly heavy. like every morning i wake up and the thought of just... existing... is too much. the lab failed again, the funding is gone, and i feel like there's nothing left of me. i'm just so tired of fighting. i just want everything to be quiet.",
