      "content": "hotlines and groups... it's just more noise. more people trying to patch up a sinking ship. i'm not looking for a way to \"cope\" or \"manage\" the weight anymore. that's what i've been doing for years and it hasn't worked. i'm just so profoundly tired of the cycle. i look at the possibility of just... not being here, of just having everything stop, and it's the only thing that feels like it would actually bring any peace. it feels like the only way to finally get some rest.",
